      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks, but the resources dont really change the reality. like, they talk about managing it or coping, but that just feels like more work. more effort just to reach a baseline of barely surviving. i just keep thinking about how quiet it would be if things just... stopped. no more meds, no more doctors, no more waiting for the next flare up. just peace.",
